Good to hear about space.....we increased our clinic space...as we have 4 dental chairs instead of 3...as to decrese waiting time...but if patient won't intimate or patient coming late by half an hour,from the appointment time ...we are unable to do check up on time and request generously to wait for his or her diagnosis as we believe in quality treatment for all our patients ...not the quantity...
water we change for each patient and even patient has the easy accessibility for water change while sitting on dental chair...as we provide RO purified water and good quality disposable glass for every patient both in working and reception area...
our clinic is the only clinic in north and West Delhi with Anti Bacterial Membrane facility ....done every 3 months and Bio Medical waste disposal as well...even after charging lowest Consultation charges...
But yes yr feedback helps us to improve...as out of more than 98 percent positive feedback...
negative feedback helps us to learn and helps us to do better for our patients......
